{"tid":945521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北方四島爭端 俄宣布島上已建新軍營","createTime":"2018-12-18T03:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T04:21:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53217d2f19fbfcb948703a5ae7a05007a52162fc","tid":945521,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20181218/042956684043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20181218%2F042956684043.jpg&h=e0cd8896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄國國防部聲明指出，莫斯科當局計劃將把軍隊移往南千島群島其中2個島嶼上的4個營區。南千島群島即是日本所說的北方四島。（<a href=\"http://圖取自Google地圖網頁google.com/maps）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAGoogle%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81google.com%2Fmaps%EF%BC%89&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f4616956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自Google地圖網頁google.com/maps）</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社莫斯科17日綜合外電報導）俄羅斯政府今天指出，他們已在靠近日本的爭議性北方四島上建造新軍營，並會為裝甲車輛興建更多設施。日本曾敦促俄國減少當地的軍事活動，如今這項舉動可能激怒東京當局。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，俄國國防部聲明指出，莫斯科當局計劃下週把軍隊移往南千島群島（Southern Kurils）其中2個島嶼上的4個營區。<br />\n<br />\n南千島群島即是日本所說的北方四島（Northern Territories），包括擇捉島、國後島、色丹島、齒舞群島4個島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n克里姆林宮近日指出，日本首相安倍晉三可能會在明年1月21日訪問俄國，就在兩國試圖努力化解北方四島領土爭議之際，卻傳出俄國在北方四島建造新軍營的消息。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府沒有立即發表回應。東京當局今年7月指出，他們曾要求俄國減少在北方四島的軍事活動，但莫斯科當局忽視這項請求。<br />\n<br />\n蘇俄軍隊在第二次世界大戰即將結束時占領北方四島，如今莫斯科和東京當局都宣稱擁有這4島主權。<br />\n<br />\n雙方外交官都談過恢復1956年「日蘇共同宣言」的可能性，當年這份宣言明訂，只要兩國簽署和平條約，蘇俄將歸還齒舞群島及色丹島給日本。<br />\n<br />\n俄國總統蒲亭（Vladimir Putin）曾與安倍晉三舉行多次當面會談，試圖在這件事取得進展。（譯者：陳彥鈞/核稿：張曉雯）1071218<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201812180044.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201812180044.aspx&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=52ec7f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201812180044.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n好似玩AOC起個兵營係人地門口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9302b7e44b488831a70ea97aedcbe6b163aa6220","tid":945521,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"得閒又揾d野搞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa212369cf6565c3abea0a8851a6de54d00b5a50","tid":945521,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"又話日俄友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b6382368c18c3463f08f2d404bfa1d26eb90ac","tid":945521,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9n5ySY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9n5ySY.png&h=06a3ea6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/阿伊努族\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%98%BF%E4%BC%8A%E5%8A%AA%E6%97%8F&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b597a522\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/阿伊努族</a><br />\n<br />\n幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個地方 日文同俄語都係通用語"},{"pid":"b82b24081c3a4c8d64c43da8797e0d82c71da41a","tid":945521,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUoo43r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUoo43r.png&h=b79f43ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}